Continue Step 1 of [ME] Design MVP — finish identifying the riskiest assumption for the email summarizer. The MVP workflow naturally feeds into LE in Step 5 (Plan Build-Measure-Learn). This is the right path if you're still scoping.
Stay in conceptual chat — keep asking me lean/MVP questions, no workflow.
My recommendation: option 2. We were one good answer away from naming your riskiest assumption. Once we have it, the experiment design (LE) is mostly a fill-in-the-blanks exercise on top.

Which one?"
